lines.text: Suhena was seen in person today for management of Gestational Diabetes and
hypothyroidism. She is currently 11 weeks gestation with an EDD May 10, 2026.
Since last seen Suhena tells me she is moving to London, Ontario within 1 week.
Fasting sugars have been improved with the start of basaglar. She is eating about a
soup bowl's size of rice with dinner. She is eating protein and veggies with her meals
and walking at home after meals.
Her blood glucose trends are as follows:
2hr PCD: 5/14 above target (eating out/large portions of rice)
Deferred as this was a virtual appointment.
